The paper discusses the use of data mining methods to identify causal relationships in large datasets, which falls under the scope of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also mentions the use of association rule mining, which is a common technique in data mining (cs.DM) and databases (cs.DB). Additionally, the paper proposes a new algorithm for mining causal rules, which could be considered a contribution to computer engineering (cs.CE).
